    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 11 — LinkedIn Prospect → CRM Pipeline\n\n**Env variables needed:**\n- PHANTOMBUSTER_API_KEY\n- PHANTOMBUSTER_AGENT_ID (your LinkedIn scraper agent ID)\n- REPLACE_WITH_HUBSPOT_TOKEN in the HTTP node (or use HubSpot credential)\n\n**Phantombuster setup:**\nUse the 'LinkedIn Sales Navigator Search Export' or 'LinkedIn Search Export' phantom. Run it before Monday 8am so output is ready.\n\n**Note:** If Phantombuster output is a URL (not inline JSON), add an HTTP Request node to fetch the output file before the Parse node.",
        "height": 628,
        "width": 1380
